#meromorphicOrderAt\">meromorphicOrderAt</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Meromorphic/Order.html#meromorphicOrderAt_of_not_meromorphicAt","kind":"theorem","line":52,"name":"meromorphicOrderAt_of_not_meromorphicAt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/Meromorphic/Order.lean#L52-L55"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">noncomputable def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Meromorphic/Order.html#meromorphicOrderAt\"><span class=\"name\">meromorphicOrderAt</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Field/Basic.html#NontriviallyNormedField\">NontriviallyNormedField</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#NormedAddCommGroup\">NormedAddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Basic.html#NormedSpace\">NormedSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> → <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/TypeTags.html#WithTop\">WithTop</a> <a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">ℤ</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The order of a meromorphic function `f` at `z₀`, as an element of `ℤ ∪ {∞}`.\n\nThe order is defined to be `∞` if `f` is identically 0 on a neighbourhood of `z₀`, and otherwise the\nunique `n` such that `f` can locally be written as `f z = (z - z₀) ^ n • g z`, where `g` is analytic\nand does not vanish at `z₀`. See `MeromorphicAt.meromorphicOrderAt_eq_top_iff` and\n`MeromorphicAt.meromorphicOrderAt_eq_int_iff` for these equivalences.\n\nIf the function is not meromorphic at `x`, we use the junk value `0`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Meromorphic/Order.html#meromorphicOrderAt","kind":"def","line":39,"name":"meromorphicOrderAt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/Meromorphic/Order.lean#L39-L50"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Analysis.Meromorphic.Basic","Mathlib.Algebra.Order.WithTop.Untop0"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.Analysis.Meromorphic.Order"}